as we get them ready for you in about 5-7 minutes!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<em><strong>Go ahead, call us a “genie” who makes your Hadoop wishes come true!</strong></em>','What’s in it?','','inherit','open','open','','355-autosave','','','2012-04-24 22:23:18','2012-04-24 22:23:18','',355,'http://www.clusterstogo.com/355-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
